sentences: John Dirne (born 14 September 1981), better known by his stage name John Christian, is a Dutch DJ, record producer and musician from Amsterdam.
He has been active since 2012 and is a former student of the Dutch Academy of Music.
He was unveiled in January 2013 with his remix of "I Could be the One" which entered the top 100 established by Beatport.
He founded his label Freeway Recordings in November 2015.
